---
title: Macadamia-Crusted Chicken & Bacon Greens with Parmesan Mash & Black Garlic Sauce
description: Long after you’ve finished this meal, you’re going to remember the way it was beautifully tied together with the creamiest black
garlic sauce. Its unique sweet, savoury and umami-packed flavour works wonderfully with succulent chicken and a side of bacon
and macadamia-adorned baby broccoli and greens.
